GIFF-ITI is digitally animated street art
created by UK artist INSA. He paints, takes

00:02:42.550 --> 00:02:47.880
a photo, and repaints multiple times to create
motion and then brings it to the internet

00:02:47.880 --> 00:02:49.970
as an animated GIFF.&nbsp;

