Volume and Noise is an interactive social
media project by Sean Hathaways that consists

00:02:57.930 --> 00:03:16.510
of a 30's Philco radio modified to speak tweets
in real time...

00:03:16.510 --> 00:03:21.570
ZIC ZAZOU is a group of musicians from France
that make music using everyday objects. Here

00:03:21.570 --> 00:03:44.180
they are playing "Habanera" from the classic
Opera Carmen...&nbsp;

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:49.950
Engineering student James McVay built MechBass,
a robotic bass guitar that consists of four

00:03:49.950 --> 00:04:08.760
string units on an aluminum frame. Here it
is playing "Hysteria" by muse.

00:04:08.760 --> 00:04:14.210
